# Cesium ion access token. Free signup at https://cesium.com/ion/.
# Vite exposes only VITE_-prefixed env vars to the client; this var
# satisfies the WS-501 "CESIUM_ION_TOKEN" requirement under that convention.
# Leave empty to fall back to the unauthenticated Cesium default scene
# (the smoke test will not pass terrain/imagery quality bars without a token).
VITE_CESIUM_ION_TOKEN=
